Package controller.officer.template

Interface IOfficerMakeEnquiry

All Known Implementing Classes:
OfficerMakeEnquiry
public interface IOfficerMakeEnquiry
A functional interface that defines the enquiry making capability for an officer in the BTO system. This is a pure interface with no implementation. It is intended to be implemented by helper classes.
